{
  "doc_id": "16325",
  "text": "Besides plasma exchange, IVIg is currently the only proven immunomodulatory treatment in GBS The standard dose of IVIg (0.4 g/kg/day over 5 days) used is empirically based on experience from the treatment of other autoimmune diseases [CITATION_1] . Alternative treatment regimens of IVIg delivering the drug over a shorter period of days have been tested in smaller trials, without showing a clear benefit for the shorter treatment interval [CITATION_2] ].",
